OL,3,CNI's Department of Health preparing
OL,4,Cfor disposable vape ban
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's Department of
OL,7,FHealth 'will make the necessary
OL,8,Fpreparations' to allow any new
OL,9,FStormont Executive to change the laws
OL,10,Faround smoking and vaping in Northern
OL,11,FIreland.
OL,13,FIt comes asJPrime Minister Rishi Sunak
OL,14,Fannounced the plan to implement the
OL,15,Fban ` using powers already in place
OL,16,Funder the Environmental Protection Act
OL,17,F` which is expected to come into force
OL,18,Fat the end of 2024 or the start of
OL,19,F2025, during a visit to a school on
OL,20,FMonday.
