OL,3,CNI's Department of Health preparing
OL,4,Cfor disposable vape ban
OL,6,FIt forms part of the Government's
OL,7,Fresponse to its consultation on
OL,8,Fsmoking and vaping, which was launched
OL,9,Fin October last year.
OL,11,FIn Northern Ireland, the decision must
OL,12,Fbe agreed by the Northern Ireland
OL,13,FAssembly, which is not sitting after
OL,14,Fpower sharing at Stormont collapsed
OL,15,Falmost two years ago.
