OL,3,CNI's Department of Health preparing
OL,4,Cfor disposable vape ban
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's Department of
OL,7,FHealth noted the UK government's plans
OL,8,Fand said: "The department will make
OL,9,Fthe necessary preparations to allow
OL,10,Fincoming ministers and the NI Assembly
OL,11,Fto take a decision on introducing the
OL,12,Fregulations in Northern Ireland."
OL,14,FThe Department of Health statement
OL,15,Fcontinued: "The Department of Health
OL,16,Fhas a long-standing strategic aim for
OL,17,Fa tobacco-free Northern Ireland.
OL,19,F"Tobacco use continues to cause around
OL,20,F2,200 deaths in Northern Ireland each
OL,21,Fyear.
