OL,3,CNI's Department of Health preparing
OL,4,Cfor disposable vape ban
OL,6,F"Alongside the immeasurable human
OL,7,Fcosts, our hospitals spend
OL,8,Fapproximately #200 million treating
OL,9,Ftobacco related conditions each year.
OL,11,F"Tobacco use is a huge threat to
OL,12,Fpublic health, but it is a threat that
OL,13,Fis entirely preventable."
OL,15,FNew data shows the number of children
OL,16,Fvaping in the last three years has
OL,17,Ftripled, the Government said, adding
OL,18,Fthat use among younger children is
OL,19,Falso rising, with 9% of 11 to 15 year-
OL,20,Folds now using vapes.
