OL,3,CNI's Department of Health preparing
OL,4,Cfor disposable vape ban
OL,6,FThe ban also aims to have a positive
OL,7,Fimpact on the environment as five
OL,8,Fmillion disposable vapes are thrown
OL,9,Faway each week, up from 1.3 million
OL,10,Ffrom last year.
OL,12,FJoseph Carter, Head of Asthma + Lung
OL,13,FUK Northern Ireland said: "Smoking is
OL,14,Fthe biggest cause of lung disease
OL,15,Fdeaths, and we don't want to see
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland being left behind.
OL,18,F"The Scottish and Welsh Governments
OL,19,Fhave already consented to Westminster
OL,20,Flegislating despite being a devolved
OL,21,Farea.
